body:
All Versions

  • Added Top Users tab to Users page to show who is using the application the most and what activities they do the most.
  • Removed duplicate provider degrees that appear on results and profile pages in some cases.
  • Fixed radius search bug that caused an invalid input error when a space was added after the miles input.

Network360 Only

  • Fixed 'Invalid provider type' error that showed up on overlap quadrant of Compare Networks page for projects with specialty mappings that don't include Specialists
